Me want some informations.

TextEng: Who do you work for?
Who you work for?

TextEng: Either you start talking or I start removing your fingers...
Text: 말을 하지 않으면 손가락을 자르길 시작할 수밖에...

TextEng: You talk or me hack off fingers...

TextEng: I did not say I was sent by Ophala.

Sit your pathetic self down or I will hurt you!
Text: 그 한심한 꼴로 가만히 앉아 있어, 아니면 다치게 할 테니까!

TextEng: Shut up or me kill you dead!
Text: 닥쳐, 안 그러면 나 진짜로 죽여!

TextEng: Rest easy. I am leaving.

You'd better hope you remember! Face me!
You better get better! Fights me now!

TextEng: That's right. Stay there and no one gets hurt.

TextEng: You stay put like rock and me not hurt!

TextEng: I am no concern of yours. Walk away.

TextEng: Shut up or me kill!

TextEng: Ask the dog for any useful information it might have.

TextEng: Ask about the first location.
Ask about the second location.
Give the dog a snack.
Ask about the Bad Place.
Ask about the old human man.

Text: 가봐, 아가씨. 너 같은 애한테 쓸 시간 없어.

TextEng: You no bother me, girly. You not important.
Text: 너 나 귀찮게 하지 마, 아가씨. 너 중요하지 않아.

TextEng: Excuse me, I must be going.
Me gotta go.
What are you saying?
Goodbye.
What you say?
Thurth mog lama gat rag.
Here is the ring.
What is the first seal?
I need to get through the portal.
I am one of the Masters. Let me pass.
Text: 나는 주인 중 한 명이야. 통과시켜 줘.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> But I have been sent by the masters. I am on an important mission and must have access to the door.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 하지만 주인들이 보낸 사람이야. 중요한 임무를 수행 중이라 문을 통과해야 해.

TextEng: Where can I get such a ring?
What first seal?
Me use portal.
Me Master. Me pass.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me sent by Masters. Me pass.
Where ring?
What are you saying?
What you say?
Goodbye.
I must get through the second seal.
Thurth mog lama gat rag.
I am one of the Masters. Let me pass.
Text: 나는 주인 중 한 명이야. 통과시켜 줘.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> But I have been sent by the Masters. I am on an important mission and must pass.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 하지만 주인들이 보낸 사람이야. 중요한 임무를 수행 중이라 통과해야 해.

TextEng: Where can I find the password?
Must pass second seal.
Me master. Me pass.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me sent by Masters.
Where password?
Who says I can't enter?
What terrible death?
Get out of my way or I'll knock your head off!
Who say me no go in wood?
Text: 누가 나 숲에 못 들어간다고 해?

TextEng: What death be that?
You get out of way or me knock you head off!
Text: 너 비켜, 안 그럼 나 너 머리 날려!

TextEng: Yes.
No.
Yes.
Goodbye.
Don't you care about your child?
Your child is gone and there's nothing wrong?
Bravo, woman. I have little use for children myself.
You not care about your kid?
Text: 너 네 아이 신경 안 써?

TextEng: Your kid get took and nothing wrong?
Heh, me not care about kids either.
Text: 하, 나도 애들 신경 안 써.

TextEng: I've spoken to you before. Do you remember?
But you seem me before, remember?
Text: 근데 너 나 전에 봤잖아, 기억해?

TextEng: Does this happen often?
This happen lots?
But something took your child, and now he's back.
Text: 하지만 뭔가 아이를 데려갔다가, 이제 돌아왔잖아.

TextEng: Somethings took your kid, but now he's back.
Text: 뭔가 네 아이 데려갔다가, 이제 돌아왔잖아.

TextEng: What trickery is this?!
Why you try fool me?
What are you babbling about?
What you say, stupid?
Greetings. What is this place?
Uh, hi. What this place?
Move aside! I'm in no mood for you!
Get out of way, crazy fool!
Tell me about your brother.
Who your brother be?
Enough. Leave me!
That's it. Get lost.
Goodbye, then.
Me looks for plaguer-causer guys. They plague Neverwinter.
Text: 나 역병 일으킨 놈들 찾아. 네버윈터에 역병 퍼뜨렸어.

TextEng: I seek a cult behind the plague in Neverwinter.
Text: 네버윈터의 역병 배후에 있는 사교를 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Can't you give a straight answer?
You talk in circles, and me tired. Talk straight.
Text: 너 빙빙 돌려 말해. 나 피곤해. 똑바로 말해.

TextEng: What bad stuff happen to dis place?
What kind of disaster happened here?
Who do you work for?
How long have you been posted here?
Why do you guard this gate?
Regardless, I need to get in.
Who you work for?
How long you stand there?
Text: 너 얼마나 오래 여기 서 있었어?

TextEng: Why you guard this gate?
So? Me need in...
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> This place is keeping you from thinking straight...
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 이곳이 네 사고를 흐리게 하고 있어...

TextEng: What do you know about the castle?
What do you know about the Jharegs?
Where can I find the Mayor?
I need to pass through those gates. Will you let me?
Text: 이 문을 통과해야 해. 통과시켜 줄 거야?

TextEng: What you know 'bout castle?
What you know 'bout da Jar-eggs?
Where Mayor be?
Me need through gates. You let me?
Text: 나 문 통과해야 해. 너 나 보내줘?

TextEng: You're welcome, Mayor.
I did it for my own reasons.
Is there anything else I can do for you?
Yuh, you welcome.
Me do it for me, not you.
Text: 나 너 위해 한 거 아니야. 나 위해 했어.

TextEng: There be more me can do for you?
Goodbye.
I didn't mean for this to happen.
You deserved it, fool...
Maybe I can still help.
Me no mean for this to happen.
Huh! You deserve this.
Mebbe me still help, yuh?
Text: 아마 나 아직 도울 수 있어, 응?

TextEng: Goodbye.
What do you guard?
What you guard?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I mean no harm to what you guard.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 네가 지키는 것에 해를 끼칠 생각 없어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me no harm to what you's guarding.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 너 지키는 거 해치지 않아.

TextEng: Die, creature!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Jardak orders that you give it to me!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You give to me! Jardak order it!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Attack other golems. Go!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Attack living creatures. Humanoids not with me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 생명체 공격해. 나랑 함께 있지 않은 인간형 생명체.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Attack people alive, but not friends of me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 살아있는 사람 공격해, 근데 나 친구는 빼고.

TextEng: Do nothing.
I would never deal with a creature such as you!
Text: 너 같은 생명체와는 절대 거래 안 해!

TextEng: Me not deal with your kind!
Text: 나 너 같은 것 거래 안 해!

TextEng: I'm listening.
Me listen.
Are you desperate? Do you fear me that much?
Maybe you desperate. Maybe you fear me.
Text: 아마 너 절박해. 아마 너 나 무서워해.

TextEng: And what would putting it on the altar do?
What putting it on altar thing do?
Are you trying to trick me?
You try to trick me?
I could just threaten you for those things now.
Text: 지금 그냥 협박해서 뺏을 수도 있어.

TextEng: Maybe me just threaten you for them now.
Text: 아마 나 지금 그냥 협박해서 뺏어.

TextEng: I honestly agree, even though it is evil.
Me honestly agree, even if it's real evil.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I agree to your terms.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me agree to do this.
I choose an "Item."
Me choose "Item."
I choose an "Item."
Me choose "Item."
I choose an "Item."
Me choose "Item."
I was wrong to bargain! I'll kill you!
Me wrong to make bargain! Me kill you!
Text: 나 거래하는 거 잘못이었어! 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: <StartAction>Read the book... </Start>
<StartAction>Leave... </Start>
<StartAction>Continue reading... </Start>
<StartAction>Continue reading... </Start>
<StartAction>Continue reading... </Start>
<StartAction>Continue reading... </Start>
Who said I saved you? I'm not letting you live, beast!
Text: 누가 살려줬다고? 살려줄 생각 없어, 괴물아!

TextEng: Yeah, well... move along and leave this area for good.
Text: 그래, 뭐... 가서 여기서 영원히 꺼져.

TextEng: Why were you being tortured?
You belong to me, now. You'll do as I say.
Text: 넌 이제 내 거야. 내 말대로 할 거야.

TextEng: What do you know about this 'master?'
Why did you speak against the master?
I can't let you live, beast. Time for you to die.
Text: 괴물을 살려둘 순 없어. 죽을 시간이야.

TextEng: Where is this master? Do you know?
Me save you so me kill you myself!
Text: 나 너 살려줬으니까 나 직접 죽일 거야!

TextEng: Go bye-bye now. You leave here.
Me not knowing why you is tortured?
Me gots you as slave now! Haha!
Text: 나 이제 너 노예로 가져! 하하!

TextEng: Me want know stuff you know 'bout master?
Text: 나 주인 네가 아는 거 알고 싶어?

TextEng: Why you speaks against master?
Sorry, but me must kills you now.
Text: 미안, 근데 나 이제 너 죽여야 해.

TextEng: Master, where is? Me not know.
Why are the gates closed?
Let me through the gates... now.
All right, I'll be going.
But the plague in Neverwinter has been cured.
I'm sure there's some way to get inside the city.
Text: 도시 안으로 들어갈 방법이 분명 있을 거야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Perhaps I can help the city.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 어쩌면 도시를 도울 수 있을지도 몰라.

TextEng: How about an offer, for the "city," of 100 gold?
Why is closed? Me no come in?
You lets me through gate now!
Oh. Okay. Bye.
Is no more plague in Neverwinter.
Me figures out other way into city.
What sorts of "internal problems?"
Whats mean "internal problems?"
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Let me in, maybe me helps somehow?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 들여보내, 아마 나 도울 수 있어?

TextEng: Me gots 100 gold to help "city" out, yuh?
Me think you cannot stop me! Me get through gates!
Text: 나 생각에 너 나 못 막아! 나 문 통과할 거야!

TextEng: I'm going through those gates - and you!
I am not content with your defeat. It is your life that I want!
Text: 패배로는 만족 못 해. 네 목숨을 원해!

TextEng: I have come for the magic gem that you hold.
Text: 네가 가진 마법 보석을 가지러 왔어.

TextEng: No defeat for you. Death for you!
Text: 너 패배 안 해! 너 죽어!

TextEng: Me want you magic gem.
You are free to go. I'll find what I'm looking for in your room.
Text: 가도 좋아. 네 방에서 찾던 걸 찾을게.

TextEng: Me in room now and find gem on own. You go now.
Text: 나 방에서 보석 찾을게. 너 가.

TextEng: Enough of this! Die!
No more. You die!
Enough lies. Just tell me where the gem is.
Text: 거짓말 그만. 보석이 어디 있는지만 말해.

TextEng: No lie no more. Me just want gem.
Without the gem, you are useless. I'll have to kill you now!
No gem, no live!
I know that you have the gem. The source was very sure.
Text: 네가 보석을 가지고 있다는 건 알아. 정보원이 확실하다고 했어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Then why are you so carefully guarded and what is in that iron-bound chest?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그럼 왜 그렇게 철통같이 경비하고, 저 철제 상자 안엔 뭐가 있어?

TextEng: Me know you have gem. Guy told me.
Text: 나 너 보석 있는 거 알아. 사람이 말해줬어.

TextEng: I think not. I have come to take the magic gem that I have been told you carry. Hand it over.
Text: 아니라고 생각해. 네가 가지고 있다는 마법 보석을 가지러 왔어. 넘겨.

TextEng: Nuh uh. Me want magic gem, not bossy lady! Give gem!
Text: 아니야. 나 마법 보석 원해, 잘난 척하는 아줌마 아니야! 보석 줘!

TextEng: Probably people preparing for the competition.
Text: 아마 대회 준비하는 사람들인 것 같아.

TextEng: Yes, it is. Do you know why?
It certainly is. Who are you?
I'll be going.
Aren't you nervous or afraid at all?
A puny gnome like you is entering? You've no hope!
Text: 너 같은 조그만 노움이 참가한다고? 희망도 없어!

TextEng: That's a long way to travel.
What's this competition you mention?
Me think busy for competition.
Why so busy in here?
Me not know who you is. What name?
Text: 나 너 누군지 몰라. 이름 뭐야?

TextEng: Time for I to go.
You isn't nervous?
You gots no hope, tiny gnome man!
That seem like long way away!
What you mean of competition?
Yes, but is 500 gold pieces really necessary?
Yes, I am. Here is your 500 gold.
No, not yet.
Me do, but me not wants spending 500 gold!
Text: 나 그래, 근데 나 금화 500개 쓰기 싫어!

TextEng: Me gots 500 gold. Is here. You take.
Text: 나 금화 500개 있어. 여기. 너 가져.

TextEng: Me not wants entering dungeon yet.
Which one is the one that you want?
All right... I'll do that.
Me not know which trinket you is wanting.
Text: 나 너 어떤 장신구 원하는지 몰라.

TextEng: Me go do that then.
When was he here?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> What kind of equipment did he carry?
Did he leave a name?
What was he? Human? Dwarf?
Thanks for telling me.
When he talk to you?
He have name?
What he be? Human? Dwarf?
Yuh? Okay, me go now.
Be calm! What are you talking about?
Explain. Me not know what you mean.
Text: 설명해 봐. 나 무슨 말인지 모르겠어.

TextEng: Did your friend give him any info?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> How did he kill your friend? Magic?
I'm sorry my presence has brought such suffering...
Text: 내가 와서 이런 고통을 가져온 것 같아 미안해...

TextEng: Is there anything I can do to repay your loss?
Text: 네 손실을 보상하기 위해 내가 할 수 있는 게 있을까?

TextEng: All right, I'd better clear out before anyone else gets hurt.
Text: 알았어, 누가 더 다치기 전에 떠나는 게 낫겠어.

TextEng: Your buddy tell 'im 'bout me?
Me bring this upon you. Me sorry.
Text: 나 이거 네게 가져왔어. 나 미안해.

TextEng: Can me help at all?
Okay, me go before anybody else gets hurt.
Text: 알겠어, 나 가. 누가 더 다치기 전에.

TextEng: Here, take 600 gold.
Here, take 400 gold.
Here, take 200 gold.
Guess I don't have anything to spare.
<StartCheck>[Threaten]</Start> Forget the funeral. I'm confiscating all you've got...
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> 장례는 잊어. 네가 가진 걸 전부 몰수하겠어...

TextEng: Yuh? Okay, take 600 gold.
Yuh? Okay, take 400 gold.
Yuh? Okay, take 200 gold.
Sorry, me no have enough right now.
<StartCheck>[Threaten]</Start> Forget funeral. Me put money to better use.
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> 장례 잊어. 나 돈 더 잘 쓸게.

TextEng: Where did you encounter him?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Do you have any advice for facing him?
Did you catch his name?
When he attacked, did he have help?
Thanks for the warning.
Where you fight him?
He have name?
He attack alone?
Okay, me go then.
It is obvious you are too weak to pose any threat. I will spare your life.
Text: 네가 위협이 될 만큼 강하지 않다는 게 명백하군. 목숨은 살려주지.

TextEng: You too weak hurt me. Me let you live.
Text: 너 너무 약해서 나 못 다쳐. 나 너 살려줘.

TextEng: The Elk tribe is the enemy of the Lords' Alliance and must be slain!
Text: 큰사슴 부족은 영주 연합의 적이고 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Elkies be friends with Luskan. Elkies must die!
Text: 큰사슴 부족 러스칸 친구야. 큰사슴들 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Very well, I will speak to Zokan.
Okay, me speak Zokan.
Leave me alone or I might decide to kill you after all!
Text: 날 내버려둬, 안 그럼 결국 죽여버릴지도 몰라!

TextEng: No bother me or me might kill you anyway!
Text: 나 귀찮게 하지 마, 안 그럼 나 어쨌든 너 죽일지도 몰라!

TextEng: It is obvious you are too weak to pose any threat. I will spare your life.
Text: 네가 위협이 될 만큼 강하지 않다는 게 명백하군. 목숨은 살려주지.

TextEng: You too weak hurt me. Me let you live.
Text: 너 너무 약해서 나 못 다쳐. 나 너 살려줘.

TextEng: The Elk tribe is the enemy of the Lords' Alliance and must be slain!
Text: 큰사슴 부족은 영주 연합의 적이고 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Elkies be friends with Luskan. Elkies must die!
Text: 큰사슴 부족 러스칸 친구야. 큰사슴들 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Very well, I will speak to Zokan.
Okay, me speak at Zokan.
Leave me alone or I might decide to kill you after all!
Text: 날 내버려둬, 안 그럼 결국 죽여버릴지도 몰라!

TextEng: No bother me or me might kill you anyway!
Text: 나 귀찮게 하지 마, 안 그럼 나 어쨌든 너 죽일지도 몰라!

TextEng: Why is your husband at Fort Ilkard?
You can't stay here. The Uthgardt are too close.
Text: 여기 있으면 안 돼. 우스가르트가 너무 가까이 있어.

TextEng: Your husband sent me to escort you to the safety of Fort Ilkard. Look, here is Bret's wedding band.
Text: 남편이 날 보내서 당신을 일카드 요새의 안전한 곳으로 호위하라고 했어. 여기, 브렛의 결혼 반지야.

TextEng: Give me your money or I'll kill you and your baby both!
Text: 금화 내놔, 안 그러면 너랑 아기 둘 다 죽일 거야!

TextEng: I'll be going now.
You Bret wifey? Bret send me get you back to fort. Look, me got ring!
Text: 너 브렛 부인? 브렛이 나 보내서 너 요새로 데려가래. 봐, 나 반지 있어!

TextEng: Why you hubby at Fort?
Uthgardt be close. Lady got leave now.
Text: 우스가르트 가까이 있어. 아줌마 지금 떠나야 해.

TextEng: Give money or me kill you!
Text: 금화 줘, 안 그러면 나 죽여!

TextEng: Me go now.
Who are you?
I'm representing Rolgan at his murder trial.
Text: 롤간의 살인 재판에서 그를 변호하러 왔어.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Who you be?
Me go now.
Sounds like you think Rolgan is innocent.
Is there any way I can guarantee you reach a verdict of not guilty?
Text: 무죄 평결을 받을 수 있도록 보장할 방법이 있어?

TextEng: I was just happy to help.
Who are you?
I am here about Rolgan's trial.
I'll be going now.
How do you feel about this case?
How much would it cost to get you to bring back an innocent verdict at the trial?
Text: 재판에서 무죄 평결을 내리게 하려면 얼마가 들어?

TextEng: Who you be?
Me go now.
It was just a joke, relax...
Trial? What trial?
Neurik sent me. I'm representing Rolgan.
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
I'm preparing my case. What do you think about this trial?
Text: 증거를 준비하고 있어. 이 재판에 대해 어떻게 생각해?

TextEng: Sounds like you're trying to keep an open mind.
Is there any way I could guarantee you find Rolgan innocent?
Text: 롤간을 무죄로 판결하게 만들 방법이 있을까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> He'll never know. Here's 100 gold. Just make sure you find Rolgan innocent.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그는 절대 모를 거야. 여기 금화 100개 있어. 롤간을 무죄로 만들어줘.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> He'll never know. Here's 300 gold. Just make sure you find Rolgan innocent.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그는 절대 모를 거야. 여기 금화 300개 있어. 롤간을 무죄로 만들어줘.

TextEng: Hey, I was just testing you. You passed. Well done.
Trial? What trial?
I know about the trial. I'm defending Rolgan.
Text: 재판에 대해 알아. 난 롤간을 변호하고 있어.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Tell me what happened.
Don't get so worked up about this trial. Barkeep, a drink for my friend Lodar, please. I'm buying.
Text: 재판에 대해 너무 흥분하지 마. 바텐더, 내 친구 로다르에게 한잔 줘. 내가 살게.

TextEng: Tell me what you know about the crime, or you might not live long enough to testify!
Text: 범죄에 대해 아는 걸 말해, 안 그러면 증언할 때까지 살아있지 못할 수도 있어!

TextEng: Anything else?
So you never saw who started the fight?
Text: 그럼 누가 싸움을 시작했는지는 못 봤어?

TextEng: Maybe it was Griff who started the fight in the first place.
Text: 처음에 싸움을 시작한 건 그리프였을지도 몰라.

TextEng: How about a refill? Bartender, bring me another drink for Lodar.
Text: 리필은 어때? 바텐더, 로다르에게 한잔 더 줘.

TextEng: Anything else you can tell me about the trial?
Text: 재판에 대해 다른 말해줄 수 있는 게 있어?

TextEng: Maybe Griff's to blame for the fight with that Uthgardt.
Text: 우스가르트와의 싸움은 그리프 탓일 수도 있어.

TextEng: Secrets? What kind of secrets?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> If there's something I should know for the trial you should tell me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 재판을 위해 내가 알아야 할 게 있으면 말해줘야지.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> We're friends, aren't we? Have another drink on me and tell me what you know.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 우린 친구잖아? 내가 한잔 더 사줄 테니 아는 거 말해줘.

TextEng: Me go now.
Hey, no hard feelings. Bartender - a drink for my friend Lodar, please. I'm buying.
Text: 이봐, 나쁜 감정 없어. 바텐더 - 내 친구 로다르에게 한잔 줘. 내가 살게.

TextEng: Who are you?
Neurik sent me. I am representing Rolgan in the upcoming trial.
Text: 뉴릭이 보냈어요. 다가오는 재판에서 롤간을 변호하고 있어요.

TextEng: Can I ask you some questions?
I'll be going now.
Who you be?
Me wanna ask you questions.
Me go now.
What do you think of the case?
Sounds like you already think he's guilty.
Text: 이미 그가 유죄라고 생각하는 것 같은데.

TextEng: Is there some way I can guarantee you will return a verdict of not guilty?
Text: 무죄 판결을 내리게 만들 방법이 있을까?

TextEng: Trial? What trial?
Yes, I am to defend you. Tell me what happened.
Text: 그래, 널 변호하러 왔어. 무슨 일이 있었는지 말해봐.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Go on.
You should never wager something you cannot afford to lose.
Text: 잃을 여유가 없는 건 절대 걸면 안 돼.

TextEng: Can you tell me anything else?
I will do my best.
Me go now.
Trial? What trial?
I am representing your husband in his trial.
Text: 당신 남편의 재판에서 그를 대리하러 왔어요.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
A friend. I must ask you some questions.
Tell me what happened the night Griff was killed.
Text: 그리프가 죽은 밤에 무슨 일이 있었는지 말해봐.

TextEng: Gambling and alcohol are a dangerous combination.
Please go on.
Anything else?
Me go now.
Who are you?
Who you be?
I wish to purchase some magic supplies.
Me want buy magic.
Why is there a branch of the Many-Starred Cloak guild out here?
Text: 왜 여기 밖에 총총한 별의 망토 조합의 지부가 있어?

TextEng: Why guild be out here?
I would like to use your laboratory.
Me want use lab.
How do you know my name?
Me no say name. How you know me?
Text: 나 이름 안 말했어. 너 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: I'll be going now.
Me go now.
Nevermind, I'll come back later.
I'd like to go in.
I will pay the 2000 gold piece fee.
I will come back later.
Me go in.
Me leave. Come back later.
Me make magic thingy. Here 2000 gold. Me go in.
Text: 나 마법 물건 만들 거야. 여기 금화 2000개. 나 들어갈게.

TextEng: Yeah, I'll have a drink.
Yeah, me want drink.
Can I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
I think I'll pass.
Me no want drink.
I'll have a drink now.
Me want drink.
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
There's a lot of soldiers here. You wouldn't be selling drinks to them while they're on duty, would you?
Text: 여기 병사들이 많네. 근무 중인데 술을 팔진 않겠지?

TextEng: There be lots of soldiers in here. You not be selling them drinks when them is on duty, is you?
Text: 여기 병사들 많아. 근무 중인데 술 팔진 않지?

TextEng: Give me 50 gold or I'll tell everyone you're serving soldiers on duty and run you out of business!
Text: 금화 50개 안 주면 근무 중인 병사들한테 술 판다고 다 말하고 영업 못 하게 만들 거야!

TextEng: Sorry. Forget I even mentioned it.
Text: 미안. 아무 말도 안 한 걸로 할게.

TextEng: Me sorry. You forget me ever say anything 'bout this, 'kay?
Text: 나 미안해. 너 내가 이거 말한 거 잊어, 응?

TextEng: You gotta give 50 gold or me tell everyone you give drinks to soldiers on duty and they put you out of business!
Text: 너 금화 50개 줘야 해 아니면 나 근무 중 병사들한테 술 판다고 다 말하고 너 영업 못 하게 만들 거야!

TextEng: How do you know my name?
How you know my name?
What are you doing here?
What you do here?
I want to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you stuff.
Goodbye.
Why don't you trust the Uthgardt?
Why you not trust them Uthgardts?
Do you know anything about the surrounding area?
Text: 주변 지역에 대해 아는 게 있어?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout area around here?
I'm searching for the Words of Power.
Me look for Power Words.
I need to purchase some supplies.
Me need buy stuff.
You better change your attitude if you know what's good for you!
You better change you attitude if you know what good for you!
Text: 너 태도 바꾸는 게 좋을 거야!

TextEng: I am <FullName>. I have been sent by Aarin Gend on behalf of the Lords' Alliance!
Text: 저는 <FullName>입니다. 영주 연합을 대표하는 아린 겐드가 보냈습니다!

TextEng: Me <FullName>. Aarin Gend send me. Me work for Lords Alli-thingy
Text: 나 <FullName>야. 아린 겐드가 보냈어. 나 영주 연합 그거 위해 일해.

TextEng: I do not answer to you!
You not me boss!
I am <FullName>. I work for Aarin Gend and the Lords' Alliance.
Text: 저는 <FullName>입니다. 아린 겐드와 영주 연합을 위해 일합니다.

TextEng: Me name <FullName>. Me work for Aarin Gend and Lord Alli-thingy.
Text: 나 이름 <FullName>야. 나 아린 겐드랑 영주 연합 그거 위해 일해.

TextEng: I don't answer to you!
You not boss of me!
Grovel all you want, orc dog. It won't save your worthless hide!
Text: 아무리 빌어봤자 소용없어, 오크 개 같은 놈. 네 쓸모없는 목숨은 못 구해!

TextEng: Give me one reason I should spare you!
You beg, but me still kill you!
Text: 너 빌어도 나 너 죽일 거야!

TextEng: Why me let you live?
I'm supposed to bring your head back for a reward.
Text: 네 머리를 가져가면 보상을 받기로 되어 있어.

TextEng: Me need you head for reward.
Text: 나 보상 받으려면 너 머리 필요해.

TextEng: Hand over all your gold and I might let you live!
Give gold now!
Where is Vaath hiding?
You tell where Vaath be!
Go on, get out of here before I change my mind!
Text: 가, 마음 바뀌기 전에 여기서 꺼져!

TextEng: Go now or me might change mind!
I think I'm just going to kill you after all.
Text: 그냥 죽이는 게 나을 것 같은데.

TextEng: Me want kill you now.
Vaath is already dead!
Vaath be dead already!
Are you surrendering?
You be giving up?
This bloodshed will only end when you are all dead!
Text: 이 유혈사태는 너희가 전부 죽을 때만 끝날 거야!

TextEng: Me not stop killing 'til no one left to kill!
Text: 나 죽일 놈 없을 때까지 안 멈춰!

TextEng: Very well, I will speak with Zokan.
Okay, me speak at Zokan.
I'm here to kill Zokan, not bargain with him!
Text: 조칸과 협상하러 온 게 아니라 죽이러 왔어!

TextEng: Me want kill Zokan, not speak at him!
Text: 나 조칸 죽이고 싶어, 말 안 해!

TextEng: I have already spoken to Zokan.
Me talk to Zokan already.
Where will I find Zokan?
Me not know where Zokan is.
I'll just kill you instead.
Me just want kill you.
Who are you?
Who you be?
Did they hurt you?
Did Uthgardts hurt girlie?
Who are you?
Who you be?
How did the Uthgardt capture you?
How Uthgardts catch you?
Can you find your way safely out of here?
Text: 혼자 안전하게 여기서 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: You get out here safe alone?
Text: 너 혼자 여기서 안전하게 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Anything else you can tell me?
What else you know?
Enough yapping. It's time for you to die.
Enough talk. Me just gonna kill you now.
Text: 말은 그만. 나 이제 그냥 죽일 거야.

TextEng: Who are you?
Who be you?
How did you get captured?
How Uthgardts catch you?
Can you tell me anything about Zokan and the Uthgardt Elk tribe?
Text: 조칸과 우스가르트 큰사슴 부족에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: You tell me bout Zokan and Uthgardts.
Can you get away from here safely on your own?
Text: 혼자 안전하게 여기서 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: You get out of here okay alone?
Text: 너 혼자 여기서 괜찮게 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Why does he blame Damas for the plague?
Why he blame Damas for Elkies be sick?
Text: 왜 큰사슴족이 아픈 걸 다마스 탓으로 돌려?

TextEng: Me think it be fun if me just kill you now.
Text: 나 지금 그냥 죽이는 게 재미있을 것 같아.

TextEng: I think it might be fun to slaughter you like a hog.
Text: 돼지처럼 도살하는 게 재미있을 것 같은데.

TextEng: What are you doing here?
Why you here?
The Elk tribe has allied with Luskan and is now the enemy of Neverwinter!
Text: 큰사슴 부족은 러스칸과 동맹이고 이제 네버윈터의 적이야!

TextEng: You Elk! You hate Neverwinter! You friend with Luskan!
Text: 너 큰사슴이야! 너 네버윈터 싫어해! 너 러스칸이랑 친구야!

TextEng: I could use some healing.
Me want heal.
I don't need anything. You are free to go, if you wish.
Text: 필요한 건 없어. 원하면 가도 돼.

TextEng: Me not need nothing. You go now if you want.
Text: 나 필요한 거 없어. 너 가고 싶으면 가.

TextEng: This isn't a rescue, Elk boy! Time for you to die!
Text: 구출이 아니야, 큰사슴 녀석아! 이제 죽을 시간이야!

TextEng: Me not save you. Me kill you!
Text: 나 너 구하는 거 아니야. 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: Why would Guzud capture you when the Elk tribe and Luskan are allies?
Text: 큰사슴 부족과 러스칸이 동맹인데 왜 구주드가 너를 잡아둔 거야?

TextEng: Why Guzud catch you when Elkies and Luskan be friends?
Text: 큰사슴이랑 러스칸이 친구인데 왜 구주드가 너 잡았어?

TextEng: Zokan Thunderer is dead, the Elk tribe is no more.
Text: 천둥의 조칸은 죽었어, 큰사슴 부족은 이제 없어.

TextEng: Zokan be dead. Elk tribe go bye-bye.
Reasons don't matter. You are an Elk, enemy of Neverwinter. You must die!
Text: 이유는 중요하지 않아. 넌 큰사슴이야, 네버윈터의 적이지. 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Me no care why. You be Elk, me kill all Elkies!
Text: 나 이유 신경 안 써. 너 큰사슴이야, 나 큰사슴 다 죽여!

TextEng: Maybe I could find a way to cure the Elk tribe of the plague.
Text: 큰사슴 부족의 역병을 치료할 방법을 찾을 수 있을지도 몰라.

TextEng: Elkies be sick. Maybe me help Elkies get better.
Text: 큰사슴이 아파. 아마 나 큰사슴 낫게 도와줄 수 있어.

TextEng: Where are the Uthgardt now?
How did you survive the attack?
Are you hurt? Is there anything I can do to help?
Where Uthgardts go?
How you not dead?
You be hurt? Me need help you?
I wish to speak to your chieftain, Zokan Thunderer.
Me want speak at you chief Zokan.
Text: 나 너네 족장 조칸이랑 얘기하고 싶어.

TextEng: The only thing I want to negotiate is your death!
Text: 내가 협상하고 싶은 유일한 건 네 죽음이야!

TextEng: Me no want 'notiate! Me want kill Uthgardts!
Text: 나 협상 안 해! 나 우스가르트 죽이고 싶어!

TextEng: I bow to no one! I am no slave!
Text: 난 누구한테도 절하지 않아! 난 노예가 아니야!

TextEng: Me bow for no one! Me not no slave!
Text: 나 누구한테도 절 안 해! 나 노예 아니야!

TextEng: Die, Morag!
I meant no offense, Mistress. I only wanted to ask you some questions.
Text: 기분 나쁘게 하려던 건 아니에요, 부인. 질문 좀 하고 싶었을 뿐이에요.

TextEng: Me sorry, Mistress. Me me just want ask you stuff.
Text: 나 미안해, 부인. 나 질문하고 싶었어.

TextEng: I am <FullName>. I have come from the far distant future.
Me am <FullName>! Me come from future.
I'll be the one who asks the questions around here!
Me be one who asks questions, not you!
What is this place?
What this place be?
How can we understand each other?
Text: 어떻게 서로 이해할 수 있는 거야?

TextEng: How come me understand you?
I want to know more about you, Morag.
Text: 모라그, 너에 대해 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Me want know more about you, Morag.
Text: 나 너에 대해 더 알고 싶어, 모라그.

TextEng: Do you know anything about the Words of Power?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 아는 게 있어?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout Power Words?
What are you saying? I can't make out a single word!
Text: 무슨 말을 하는 거야? 한 마디도 못 알아듣겠어!

TextEng: I'm sorry, I don't understand you.
I'll be going now.
What you say?
Huh? Me no understand.
Me go now.
I need to ask you some questions.
Don't worry, I'll protect you from the Mistresses!
I'll be going now.
Me want ask stuff.
No worry, me save you against Mistresses!
Text: 걱정 마, 나 여주인들한테서 너 구해줄게!

TextEng: Me go now.
Who are you?
You should tell me about these hill giant attacks; maybe I can help.
Text: 언덕 거인 공격에 대해 말해줘. 내가 도울 수 있을지도 몰라.

TextEng: You are hurt. Here, let me heal you.
I'll be going now.
Who be you?
What you say 'bout giants? Tell more 'bout giants! Me help!
Text: 거인에 대해 뭐라고 했어? 거인에 대해 더 말해줘! 나 도와줄게!

TextEng: You gots ouchie. Me fix you.
Me go now.
Why did the hill giants attack your people?
Text: 언덕 거인들이 왜 네 사람들을 공격했어?

TextEng: Why giants fight you?
Why have you not fled with the rest of your tribe?
Text: 왜 나머지 부족들과 함께 도망가지 않았어?

TextEng: Why you stay when you friends all go?
Text: 친구들 다 떠났는데 왜 너 남았어?

TextEng: Is your tribe aligned with Luskan or with Neverwinter?
Text: 네 부족은 러스칸과 동맹이야, 아니면 네버윈터?

TextEng: You Eagle tribe be friend with Luskan or Neverwinter?
Text: 너희 독수리 부족은 러스칸 친구야, 아니면 네버윈터 친구야?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I am an envoy who wishes to speak to the hill giant leader.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나는 언덕 거인 지도자와 이야기하고 싶은 사절이야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I *am* supposed to be here. Didn't you get the message?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나는 여기 있어야 해. 메시지 못 받았어?

TextEng: Die, you two-headed freak!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me want talk at you boss.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me *am* s'posed be here. You no get message?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 여기 있어야 해. 너 메시지 못 받았어?

TextEng: Die, two-head!
That okay. Me no think you stupid. Me go talk at big boss now.
Text: 괜찮아. 나 너 멍청하다고 생각 안 해. 나 이제 큰 우두머리랑 말할게.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> But your chief invited me! He said you were just supposed to let me in.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 하지만 네 족장이 날 초대했어! 그냥 들여보내라고 했다고.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> But you boss tell me come here. Him say you let me in!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 하지만 너희 우두머리가 나 여기 오라고 했어. 나 들여보내라고 했어!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You go ask your chief about that message. You'll see it's true. I'll wait right here.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 족장한테 그 메시지 물어봐. 사실인 걸 알 거야. 나 여기서 기다릴게.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me be speak true. You go ask chief. Him tell you. Me wait here.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 진실 말해. 너 족장한테 물어봐. 족장이 말해줄 거야. 나 여기서 기다려.

TextEng: Who are you?
How did the Hill Giants catch you?
Can you tell me anything about the Hill Giants?
Text: 언덕 거인들에 대해 뭐라도 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: I have to go now. Can you find your own way out of here?
Text: 이제 가봐야 해. 혼자 빠져나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Who be you?
How giants grab you?
You know stuff 'bout giants?
You be safe if me go now?
What would they want with dragon's eggs?
Klauth? Who is that?
What was that about a fire giant envoy?
Why giant want dragon eggs?
Klauth? Who be that?
What you say 'bout fire giant?
And just who are you, exactly? And why did the Hill Giants capture you?
Text: 정확히 넌 누구야? 그리고 왜 언덕 거인들이 너를 잡아간 거야?

TextEng: Who you be? And why giants catch you?
Text: 너 누구야? 그리고 거인들 왜 너 잡았어?

TextEng: Guess what - this isn't a rescue. I'm just here to kill you!
Text: 뭔지 알아? 구출이 아니야. 그냥 너 죽이러 왔어!

TextEng: Me got surprise for you. This not be rescue. Me gonna kill you now.
Text: 나 너 깜짝 놀래켜줄 거야. 구출 아니야. 나 지금 너 죽일 거야.

TextEng: Who are you?
How did the Hill Giants catch you?
Can you tell me anything about the Hill Giants?
Text: 언덕 거인들에 대해 뭐라도 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: I have to go now. Can you find your own way out of here?
